"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-press-releases-steven-spielberg-stars-in-nbcuniversals-opening-film-to-welcome-viewers-to-the-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Academy Award-Winning Filmmaker Narrates \\\"Land of Stories\\\" to Kick Off NBCUniversal's Coverage Just Before the Opening Ceremony  Portions of the Film to be used inPromotional Spotsacross NBCUniversal Platforms and in AMC and IMAX Theatres    Live Coverage of the Opening Ceremony Begins on Friday, July 26, at Noon ET on NBC and Peacock; and 1 pm ET on Telemundo  STAMFORD, Conn. - June 26, 2024 -Academy Award-winning directorSteven Spielbergstars in NBCUniversal's opening film that will welcome viewers to its presentation of the Games of the XXXIII Olympiad in Paris, France, this summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Networks\", \"score\": 0.999992575351194, \"rank\": 7.424704069904543e-06, \"text\": \"AMC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Networks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Networks\"}, {\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.6729372949236545, \"rank\": 0.48602180786285026, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.999998082730618, \"rank\": 1.9172721579446386e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telemundo\", \"score\": 0.999999999389729, \"rank\": 5.801599284205651e-10, \"text\": \"Telemundo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telemundo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telemundo\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"score\": 0.99999999990996, \"rank\": 8.99404214496465e-11, \"text\": \"STAMFORD\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999987771844, \"rank\": 1.2229115795174976e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2417028102834347e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998355633715, \"rank\": 1.1005840766018702e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement was made earlier today at a press event at 30 Rockefeller Center in New York City about NBCU's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999993151505, \"rank\": 6.848557277548745e-10, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As viewers get set to watch an unprecedented Opening Ceremony on Friday, July 26, Spielberg welcomes them to the Games with a four-minute film titled, \\\"Land of Stories\\\" - which showcases the Olympics as the perfect template for telling an epic story.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.021832313699e-29, \"text\": \"Spielberg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Filmed at a Universal Studios soundstage in November 2023, NBCU worked with artists at Industrial Light & Magic to transport Spielberg to Paris.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\", \"score\": 0.9983818883844442, \"rank\": 0.0016207341396271022, \"text\": \"Universal Studios\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\"}, {\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.021832313699e-29, \"text\": \"Spielberg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2417028102834347e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Steven Spielberg is one of the world's greatest storytellers,\\\" saidMolly Solomon, President and Executive Producer, NBC Olympics Production.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.25887706899925e-22, \"text\": \"Steven Spielberg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For decades we have been moved to experience the full range of human emotions through his fully immersive storytelling style.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a thrill to see Steven so excited to speak about the magic of the Olympics - from the moments we all remember to the potential of the current athletes.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels like the perfect prelude to the Paris Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shorter versions of \\\"Land of Stories\\\" will be used topromoteNBCU's coverage of the Opening Ceremony across its broadcast, cable, streaming, and social media platforms, as well as inAMCandIMAXtheatres.\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.999996673899278